caption: The image features a spiral pattern with a blue and white color scheme. The spiral is large and takes up most of the image. The text "You know? It's okay to say no" is displayed in the top left corner of the image, while the word "Motivation" is positioned in the bottom left corner. The overall theme of the image seems to be related to personal growth and self-empowerment.
